Name: Tyger, tyger, burning bright
Description: Songs that mention a beast. you know. a critter. a creacher. a little guy

Name: White Boy Gospel
Description: Songs with religious reference (not just the use of "oh lord" or "omg." Has to be a proper reference). Does not have to be by a white man I just like the genre of what I call White Boy Gospel (Paul Simon, Talking Heads, Neil Diamond, etc.) so I made it the title

Name: Bilingual
Description: Songs with at least two languages

Name: Below average
Description: Songs from a country with a population of under 40 million (40 mil is the global avg. pop. for a country)

Name: Born to be a star
Description: Songs written or recorded for movies or TV shows. Covers or previously recorded songs are okay, but the version you submit must have been done explicitly for a movie/show.

Name: Finders Keepers
Description: Songs that use found audio or samples (bits of other songs or non-musical audio)
